    <h1 style="background-color:IndianRed;">Blood Drive - Toll Gate High School</h1>
     
    <p> The Toll Gate Blood Drive is happens a couple times a year, and you can help! Here are some benefits to donating: </p>
    <ul>
      <li> It can assist in saving lives. </li>
      <li> Hospitals <em> always </em> need blood. </li>
      <li> It can help people injured in accidents, undergoing cancer treatment, and battling blood diseases, among other reasons. </li>
   
    </ul>
